title: Sophomore Preseason All State - Fifth Team
text:
Sophomore Preseason All State - Fifth Team Luke Feddersen IowaPreps.com Editor 
One of the most popular features on Iowa Preps is our preseason All State basketball teams. We take an in-depth look at Class of 2018 and name our fifth team sophomore All State team. See which of the elite athletes around Iowa made the cut as we take a look towards a winter full of hoops! Sophomore Preseason All State - Fifth Team Sergio Rodriguez, Sidney
